title: Tin Foil Hat #72: Tin Foil Hat Vs Timesuck With The Undeniable Dan Cummins
description: Thank you for tuning in for another fun weird ass episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli.   This episode Ryan and Sam welcome hilarious comic and host of the awesome podcast Timesuck, Dan Cummins!  This episode we discuss whether p*e*d*o*g*a*t*e is real or not.  Thank you for supporting this podcast.  We love all of you Mad Hatters!
